"However, once a course has been launched, and is being used by learners, "
"publishing updates should be well planned and coordinated. Firstly to "
"reduce the burden and potential confusion to users for having a lot of "
"small, regular updates and secondly, to ensure a good review can be made "
"of the content before it is made live for learners."
